project_descr: The overall objective of the project is to provide a range of coherent and integrated services and support measures in three selected municipalities Suharekë/Suva Reka, Dragash/Dragaš and Štrpce/Shtërpcë.

outputs.output_descr: To create institutional and individual capacities in target Municipalities
donor_name: PROVISIONAL INSTITUTIONS OF SELF GOVERNMENT IN KOSOVO

outputs.output_descr: Creation of new jobs and income generation opportunities through an improved market positioning and productivity of local micro and small enterprises, including individual farmers in Municipalities of Štrpce/Shtërpcë and Dragash//Dragaš.
